source:
TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_SEQ_00 Quest Sync
Grawley seems fit to explode.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_SEQ_00特殊ルール： レベルアジャスト
アミティーのグラーリーは、困り果てているようだ。

source: TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_TODO_00<tab>Place the bulging sack of foodstuffs at the designated location.
TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_TODO_01<tab>Lie in wait and defeat the hobgoblin thieves.
target: TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_TODO_01<tab><var 28 ((EObj)) F61EACC801 /var>で待機し、現れた<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2232A01 /var>を討伐
TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_TODO_02<tab>アミティーのグラーリーと話す

source: TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_GRAWLEY_000_001<tab>...Sorry, friend, that wasn't meant for you. It's those bastard hobgoblins...
target:
TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_GRAWLEY_000_001あぁ……すまん、あんたのことじゃないんだ。
おかげで、物資の管理については目途がたったんだが、
今度は、ホブゴブリンどもに迷惑していてな。

source: TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_GRAWLEY_000_002<tab>They know none of us are fighters, so they just skulk in and raid our food stores, brazen as you please! But I bet you could give them somethin' to chew on, eh?
target:
TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_GRAWLEY_000_002戦う術をもたない我々を舐めきっているのか、
大事な食料をくすねていきやがる！
あんた、腕利きなんだろう……手を貸しちゃくれないか？

source: TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_GRAWLEY_000_003<tab>Here, take this supply sack and drop it just outside the village. Once them thieving blighters come sniffing about, you spring out of hiding and unleash a storm of righteous justice!
target:
TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_GRAWLEY_000_003この「」を地面に置いて、
陰に隠れてしばらく待てば、奴らは釣られてやってくるはずだ。
「ホブゴブリン」どもを、やっつけてくれ！

source: TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_GRAWLEY_000_004<tab>Justice must be served! Set the table with that supply sack and make sure them hobgobbers get a proper helping!
target:
TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_GRAWLEY_000_004この「」を地面に置いて、
陰に隠れてしばらく待てば、奴らは釣られてやってくるはずだ。
「ホブゴブリン」どもを、やっつけてくれ！

source: TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_GRAWLEY_000_010<tab>Yes! Vengeance for our missed meals and rumbling bellies! Fine work, my friend!
target:
TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_GRAWLEY_000_010ありがてえ、奴らを倒してくれたのか！
あんた、本当に強いんだな！

source: TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_GRAWLEY_000_011<tab>Hobgoblins have plagued this island for as long as anyone can remember. They're cunning enough to make tools, but still they act like beasts─mean, filthy brutes what lack the barest shred of common decency!
target:
TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_GRAWLEY_000_011ホブゴブリンってのは、昔からコルシア島に棲んでる獣人でな。
道具を使う程度の知恵はあるが、野蛮で不潔……
その上、倫理観のカケラもないときた！

source: TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_GRAWLEY_000_012<tab>And even though you've cowed them for the moment, I fear the lesson won't stick. Oh, they'll be back. You can be sure of that.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_GRAWLEY_000_012奴らは警戒心が強いから、
これに懲りてしばらくは襲ってこないだろう。
しばらくは……な。

source: TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_GRAWLEY_000_013<tab>In the meantime, we'll need to think of a more <var 1A 02 /var>permanent<var 1A 01 /var> solution...
target:
TEXT_LUCKZI002_03538_GRAWLEY_000_013その間に、本格的な対策を練るしかないな……。
とにかくありがとう、助かったよ！
